data.description: Quick closing available! Welcome to a slice of paradise with absolutely NO HOA restrictions and the exciting possibility of SHORT-TERM RENTALS! This enchanting 2-bedroom, 2 full bathroom haven is nestled on over one-fourth of an acre, providing ample space for your gatherings in a charming, fenced backyard that's your very own private retreat and entertainers dream.Step inside, and you'll discover a home that's been lovingly revamped to its very bones by the current owners, who embarked on a full-scale renovation journey starting in 2008. This place boasts character and modern amenities galore!In the heart of the home, the kitchen welcomes you with granite countertops and a suite of electric appliances. And the beautiful laminate flooring gracefully guides you through the cozy space.Venturing into the backyard, you'll be captivated by the possibilities. A substantial 20-inch concrete slab, fully permitted, eagerly awaits your creative vision--a potential for a two-story expansion, turning your dreams into reality.Your outdoor escapades continue with a covered space that's tailor-made for savoring al fresco meals. With built-in counters, refrigerator, microwave, and oven, it's the ultimate outdoor dining experience. The sprawling concrete patio is a canvas for your outdoor furniture, ready to host multiple tables and chairs. Plus, there's a delightful private outdoor shower with hot water--a luxurious touch for your beachside retreat!But wait, there's more! The backyard also houses a 12x24 shed adorned with built-in shelving, and a convenient covered lean-to, perfect for stowing away your yard tools and trusty lawnmower. Also, an efficient well irrigation system ensures that your grass stays picture-perfect year-round.And the icing on the cake? This splendid haven is just a breezy 5-minute jaunt away from restaurants, the marina, and the most beautiful beaches. In this remarkable abode, the possibilities are endless, and the cozy charm is abundant. Make it your haven, and let the good times roll! Sellers will pay closing costs (title, doc stamps, owners title, and agent commissions).
